  "description": "Replace the current content of /workspace/buz_customize_kanban/views/product_views.xml with:\n\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\"?>\n<odoo>\n    <record id=\"product_template_kanban_view_inherit\" model=\"ir.ui.view\">\n        <field name=\"name\">product.template.kanban.inherit</field>\n        <field name=\"model\">product.template</field>\n        <field name=\"inherit_id\" ref=\"product.product_template_kanban_view\"/>\n        <field name=\"arch\" type=\"xml\">\n            <xpath expr=\"//kanban\" position=\"inside\">\n                <field name=\"product_tag_ids\"/>\n                <field name=\"qty_available\"/>\n                <field name=\"incoming_qty\"/>\n                <field name=\"outgoing_qty\"/>\n                <field name=\"kanban_available_qty\"/>\n                <field name=\"kanban_price\"/>\n            </xpath>\n            <xpath expr=\"//div[hasclass('o_kanban_record_top')]\" position=\"replace\">\n                <div class=\"o_kanban_record_top\">\n                    <div class=\"o_kanban_record_headings\">\n                        <strong class=\"o_kanban_record_title\">\n                            <field name=\"name\"/>\n                        </strong>\n                        <small class=\"o_kanban_record_subtitle text-muted\">\n                            <field name=\"name_eng\"/>\n                        </small>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"o_dropdown_kanban dropdown\">\n                        <a class=\"dropdown-toggle o-no-caret btn\" role=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-bs-display=\"static\" href=\"#\" aria-label=\"Dropdown menu\" title=\"Dropdown menu\">\n                            <span class=\"fa fa-ellipsis-v\"/>\n                        </a>\n                        <div class=\"dropdown-menu\" role=\"menu\">\n                            <t t-if=\"widget.editable\">\n                                <a role=\"menuitem\" type=\"edit\" class=\"dropdown-item\">Edit</a>\n                            </t>\n                            <t t-if=\"widget.deletable\">\n                                <a role=\"menuitem\" type=\"delete\" class=\"dropdown-item\">Delete</a>\n                            </t>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </xpath>\n            <field name=\"list_price\" position=\"attributes\">\n                <attribute name=\"invisible\">1</attribute>\n            </field>\n            <field name=\"list_price\" position=\"after\">\n                <field name=\"kanban_price\" widget=\"monetary\" options=\"{'currency_field': 'currency_id'}\"/>\n                <!-- Stock Information -->\n                <div class=\"mt-2\">\n                    <div class=\"d-flex gap-1\">\n                        <span><strong>Available:</strong></span>\n                        <span><strong><field name=\"kanban_available_qty\" widget=\"float\" options=\"{'digits': [16,2]}\"/> <field name=\"uom_id\"/></strong></span>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <!-- Product tags -->\n                <div class=\"mt-2\">\n                    <field name=\"product_tag_ids\" widget=\"many2many_tags\"/>\n                </div>\n            </field>\n        </field>\n    </record>\n</odoo>\n```\n\nWrite exactly this content. No other changes.",
